<i>noun</i>: 목마름 [몽마름], 갈증 [갈쯩] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>목마름 [몽마름]</dt><br>
<dd>1. thirst</dd><br>
<dd>물 등이 몹시 마시고 싶은 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one needs desperately to drink water, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. thirst; desire</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것을 몹시 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one hopes for something eagerly.</dd><br>
<dt>갈증 [갈쯩]</dt><br>
<dd>1. thirst</dd><br>
<dd>목이 말라 물이 마시고 싶어지는 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of someone craving water.</dd><br>
<dd>2. unfulfilled desire</dd><br>
<dd>이루거나 얻지 못한 것을 간절히 원하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of someone desperately wishing for something not achieved or obtained.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>